    "name": "Hungry Neighbors",
    "steam_appid": 3301310,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/6065ddf28592c959d7dcc3a4b540fcd4.avif?t=1734044056\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Turning away from the stress of the big city, you set sail for Horizon Island, a place far from civilisation, where a small community of residents live a simple life in tune with nature. As their new chef, you will ensure that everyone gets fed. It's not so bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Not when there's enough food to go around, at least. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/50de835066a77ac6e8fa7252b958710e.avif?t=1734044056\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras_big/50de835066a77ac6e8fa7252b958710e.avif?t=1734044056 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/62f7997a12591c97cae74a592fba9b72.avif?t=1734044056\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unravel the mystery of Horizon Island, and discover the secrets lurking beneath this happy village of friendly animals.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a variety of cooking minigames, and learn to make do when ingredients run low.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose which residents to spend time and build friendships which might just blossom into something more.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience a whole other side of your new best friends with 4 character-specific routes, each with multiple bloody conclusions.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Play over 4 seasons, each one a little less plentiful than the last.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replay to discover secret achievements which reward you for indulging your curiosity and making unconventional choices.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/74adf58f19e2ab9684e90aa21085b043.avif?t=1734044056\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras_big/74adf58f19e2ab9684e90aa21085b043.avif?t=1734044056 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/4d93099af63d002188384886a0836904.avif?t=1734044056\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get to know your neighbors in a choice-based visual novel format.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/dfe9e029578053a2703454a819a8c403.poster.avif?t=1734044056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/dfe9e029578053a2703454a819a8c403.webm?t=1734044056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/dfe9e029578053a2703454a819a8c403.mp4?t=1734044056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Explore the island in investigation segments.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/d3c157c69e9b8cee7d02284f28ed4f9d.poster.avif?t=1734044056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/d3c157c69e9b8cee7d02284f28ed4f9d.webm?t=1734044056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/d3c157c69e9b8cee7d02284f28ed4f9d.mp4?t=1734044056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Prepare delicious meals with a variety of cooking minigames.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/445d3f390a00043a476c6b6a42ae6a45.poster.avif?t=1734044056\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/445d3f390a00043a476c6b6a42ae6a45.webm?t=1734044056\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3301310/extras/445d3f390a00043a476c6b6a42ae6a45.mp4?t=1734044056\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
